  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  recurrent patellar dislocation or instability,patients with TT－TG value equal to or
             greater than 20 mm,patients with closed epiphyseal plate

        TT－TG：Two lines drawn perpendicular to posterior bicondylar line, one line through middle
        of the trochlear groove(TG) and the second through tibial tuberosity (TT). Distance between
        the lines is measured.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  bilateral patellar dislocation, a previous surgery in the involved leg,patients with
             open epiphyseal plate,patients with severe trochlear dysplasia
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
